{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, the ability of HSI reconstruction to work with incomplete data opens new frontiers in realtime monitoring and quality control in the food industry.",
    "It allows for the rapid assessment of food quality on production lines, where speed and efficiency are crucial, without the need for extensive and time-consuming data collection processes.",
    "Image reconstruction has shown great promise and found extensive use in fields such as medicine (Wang et al. 2020; Qiu et al. 2023) and remote sensing (Deng et al. 2021; Gao et al. 2021; Hu et al. 2023).",
    "Deep learning-based reconstruction algorithms have played a crucial role in enhancing diagnostic accuracy and efficiency, making medical care more reliable and intelligent (Qiu et al. 2023).",
    "HSI reconstruction is also utilized in geographical and marine applications."
  ]
}